description: This meat haven boasts a variety of yummy sandwiches and slices of your favorite cuts like roast beef, pulled pork, ground meat, smoked turkey, and roasted chicken. If you're a real meat lover be sure to try their meat on a stick - chicken, beef or pork belly served on a flour tortilla. Despite their namesake however, they do have the vegetarians covered by offering a veggie burger and yummy grilled cheese.
name: Marty's Meats
